    <td class="roweven" valign="top" width="2000">- Added values for the &quot;style&quot; attribute (CSS2 properties)<br>- Added values for CSS2 properties<br>- &lt;PageUp&gt; and &lt;PageDown&gt; are now usable to move highlight through the list<br>- When adding a value for an attribute, current attribute value (if exists) is replaced by the selected one, except for &quot;style&quot; attribute for which values are append<br>- Set g:eh_singlequote variable to 0 or 1 to use double or single quote when adding attributes (For example id=&quot;&quot; or id='')</td>
</tr>
